text: have allaha tamaro bhara halavo kare che, te khuba jane che ke tamaramam nabala'i che, basa! Jo tamaramam eka so loko dhiraja rakhanara hase, to te baso para vijaya melavase ane jo tamaramam eka hajara loko hase to te allahana adesathi be hajara para vijaya melavase, allaha dhiraja rakhanara lokoni sathe che
